---

<ShoppingLayout 
  title={`${testData.name} – Order Online | Track Your Labs`}
  description={`Order the ${testData.name} online for $${testData.price.toFixed(2)}. Evaluate liver and kidney function, electrolyte balance, and overall metabolic health with a single blood test.`}
>
  <main class="flex-1">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="min-h-screen bg-base-100">
      <div>
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4">
          <!-- Breadcrumb -->
          <nav class="text-sm breadcrumbs py-4">
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900">Home</a></li>
              <li><a href="/tests" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900">Tests</a></li>
              <li><a href="/tests#general-health" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900">General Health</a></li>
              <li class="text-gray-900">Comprehensive Metabolic Panel (CMP) Test</li>
            </ul>
          </nav>

          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">{testData.name}</h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            {testData.description}
          </p>
          
          <!-- Price and Add to Cart -->
          <div class="mb-12">
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-6">
              <span class="text-4xl font-bold">${testData.price.toFixed(0)}</span>
            </div>
            
            <button id="add-to-cart" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-16">
              Add to Cart
            </button>
          </div>

          <!-- Marketing Copy Section -->
          <div class="marketing-section">
            <div class="vertical-separator"></div>
            
            <div class="marketing-content">
              <!-- Quick Facts -->
              <div class="quick-facts-section">
                <h2 class="section-title">Quick Facts</h2>
                <table class="facts-table">
                  <tbody>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="fact-label">Test Type</td>
                      <td class="fact-value">Blood test</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="fact-label">Fasting Required</td>
                      <td class="fact-value">Yes (8–12 hours recommended)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="fact-label">Sample Type</td>
                      <td class="fact-value">{testData.sampleType}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td class="fact-label">Turnaround Time</td>
                      <td class="fact-value">{testData.turnaround}</td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>

              <!-- What This Test Measures -->
              <div class="content-section">
                <h2 class="section-title">What This Test Measures</h2>
                <p class="section-text">
                  A Comprehensive Metabolic Panel (CMP) includes 18 essential tests:
                </p>
                <ul class="benefits-list mt-4">
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Glucose</strong> — Blood sugar level to screen for diabetes and hypoglycemia</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Calcium</strong> — Essential for bone health, muscle function, and nerve signaling</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Total Protein</strong> — Overall protein status in the blood</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Albumin</strong> — Main blood protein made by the liver</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Globulin (Calculated)</strong> — Proteins important for immune function</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Albumin/Globulin Ratio</strong> — Balance between two major protein types</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Alanine Aminotransferase (ALT)</strong> — Liver enzyme that indicates liver health</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Aspartate Aminotransferase (AST)</strong> — Enzyme found in liver and heart</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Alkaline Phosphatase (ALP)</strong> — Enzyme related to liver and bone health</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Bilirubin</strong> — Waste product from red blood cell breakdown</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Blood Urea Nitrogen (BUN)</strong> — Kidney function marker</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Creatinine</strong> — Primary indicator of kidney function</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>BUN/Creatinine Ratio</strong> — Helps determine cause of kidney problems</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Estimated Glomerular Filtration Rate (eGFR)</strong> — Overall kidney function assessment</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Sodium</strong> — Electrolyte for fluid balance and nerve function</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Potassium</strong> — Critical for heart rhythm and muscle function</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Chloride</strong> — Electrolyte that helps maintain pH balance</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span><strong>Carbon Dioxide (CO₂)</strong> — Measures blood acidity and helps assess lung and kidney function</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- Who Should Take This Test -->
              <div class="content-section">
                <h2 class="section-title">Who Should Take This Test</h2>
                <ul class="benefits-list">
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Want a comprehensive health screening as part of routine care</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Have symptoms suggesting kidney or liver problems</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Are monitoring diabetes or blood sugar management</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Take medications that can affect kidney or liver function</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Need preoperative or employment health clearance</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- How It Works -->
              <div class="content-section">
                <h2 class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
                <div class="steps-container">
                  <div class="step-item">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                      <h3 class="step-title">Order Online</h3>
                      <p class="step-text">Select your test and pay securely</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="step-item">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                      <h3 class="step-title">Visit a Lab</h3>
                      <p class="step-text">Provide your sample at a Quest Diagnostics location</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="step-item">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                      <h3 class="step-title">Get Results</h3>
                      <p class="step-text">Access your secure, doctor-reviewed results within {testData.turnaround}</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- How to Prepare -->
              <div class="content-section">
                <h2 class="section-title">How to Prepare</h2>
                <ul class="benefits-list">
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Fast for 8–12 hours recommended before your appointment; only water is permitted</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.75 3.104v5.714a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-.659 1.591L5 14.5M9.75 3.104c-.251.023-.501.05-.75.082m.75-.082a24.301 24.301 0 0 1 4.5 0m0 0v5.714c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591L19.8 15.3M14.25 3.104c.251.023.501.05.75.082M19.8 15.3l-1.57.393A9.065 9.065 0 0 1 12 16a9.065 9.065 0 0 0-6.23-.307L5 14.5m14.8.8 1.402 1.402c1.232 1.232.65 3.318-1.067 3.611A48.309 48.309 0 0 1 12 21c-2.773 0-5.491-.235-8.135-.687-1.718-.293-2.3-2.379-1.067-3.61L5 14.5" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Stay well-hydrated (drink water)</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="benefit-item">
                    <svg class="benefit-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09ZM18.259 8.715 18 9.75l-.259-1.035a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.006-1.006L15.75 7.5l1.035-.259a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.006-1.006L18 5.25l.259 1.035a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.006 1.006L20.25 7.5l-1.035.259a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.006 1.006ZM16.894 20.567 16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423 1.423Z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Follow any medication guidance from your healthcare provider</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

